{"tid":456263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輾斷腳內地少女須截肢","createTime":"2017-11-02T23:41:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T19:10:37.000Z","uid":8129,"like":5,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5620ecf2a2d00d268f572585b4c77d39b2770d4e","tid":456263,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:41:02.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】十九歲內地少女前日往旺角購物，卻在過馬路時，慘遭一輛城巴撞倒，右小腿遭輾扁，經送院搶救後，小腿不保遭截肢，少女父母由內地趕來港探望表現傷心，更不敢向女兒透露已變殘廢，更擔心龐大醫療費難以負擔，要求巴士公司賠償。<br />\n<br />\n受傷少女黃曉儀（十九歲），廣州增城人，有父母及一名胞姊。胞姊已婚，與丈夫在廣州開設食肆，曉儀則在廣州入讀大專課程，常到胞姊店中幫手。<br />\n<br />\n曉儀前日受傷送院後，證實右小腿無法保留，要通宵進行截肢手術，將膝蓋以下切除。黃女父母前晚已趕抵本港，通宵陪伴女兒，至昨午二時許見女兒甦醒，始稍為寬心。但黃女今日仍要接受盆骨接駁手術。<br />\n<br />\n黃母稱，女兒是乖乖女，身材高挑，更有一雙修長美腿，今次是女兒首次來港，卻遭不幸，但她表現堅強，沒有哭過一聲。兩夫婦不敢說出截肢實情，怕她不能接受。黃母續說，因是內地人，在港醫藥費龐大，家人難以負擔，會向巴士公司追討，但對方未有前來慰問。<br />\n<br />\n城巴發言人稱，事發後曾派員到醫院，但未能接觸傷者家人，如欲索償，保險公司會作出跟進。事發前日下午四時，黃曉儀在旺角拖篋橫過亞皆老街，被一輛轉彎城巴撞倒捲入車底，右小腿遭車輪輾扁。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/K1Kzf.yZrQfYHnL_QFJUNA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTQxO2g9MTk4O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/303603.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FK1Kzf.yZrQfYHnL_QFJUNA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTQxO2g9MTk4O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F303603.jpg&h=7b65aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n城巴埋單啦仆街 咁樣剷上行人路害人一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n個人簽名 &times;按此隱藏<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\nOct 28近期活躍五毛<br />\n0群龍共舞 1天才小釣手 2三色貓 3JR 4法國佬巫斯義 <br />\n5吾系甘開心牙 6真律師何君堯 7蘇麗珊 8十卜ching <br />\n9D_wade 10RedBaron 11優美開始 12阿古路 13Romanov <br />\n14返六日唔撚易 15優美開始 16民國復興 17dewi <br />\n18侵b 19曼聯明叔 20bb chu 21小翁翁 22中出即飛天俠<br />\n23真。禁極刀 24GPDeal 25SKT三連霸冇死角<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"80a727f37af6858d3f7d26963526cf9d535c00cc","tid":456263,"uid":59511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:43:47.000Z","msg":"修長 美腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26038ad9e3d6cf55b1120c47581b79dc8a37bde5","tid":456263,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T23:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225d0df2d5474d2259cef078b4d5ba6186426333","tid":456263,"uid":47359,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T00:05:45.000Z","msg":"五毛出現<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/080535_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F080535_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1b84fe11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9efab3bf0a26a76ec473ba05f620fec0af537f48","tid":456263,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T00:23:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五毛出現<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/080535_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F080535_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1b84fe11&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n過街老屎出沒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd231543ce28e2b2ab1b641b351fc12548af6a8","tid":456263,"uid":10905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T00:59:07.000Z","msg":"截乜鬼姐撞果下都截左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我"},{"pid":"6ccacd7ee8181891e38a839512d7fc25f7cb8095","tid"